          </div>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="img/testimonial-2.jpg" alt="" />
              <div class="ml-3">
                <h5>JOHN</h5>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>
              "Having dealt with electrical issues in the past, I was skeptical about finding a reliable service provider. However, DWELLHUB exceeded
